            ],
            "subtype": "ability",
            "text": "Aiming the gnome cannons toward the enemy, loading them, and firing them requires the troop's full attention. The cannons fire a 15- foot burst of bright magic within 200 feet that deals 2d12+2 force damage (DC 22 basic Reflex save). A creature that fails their save is also dazzled for 1 round; this is a light and visual effect. The area of the explosion seems to twist and ripple for 1 minute afterward. A creature that attempts to move through the space must succeed at a DC 22 Will save or treat the area as difficult terrain; this is an illusion and visual effect.",
            "traits": [
              {
                "alternate_link": {
